My biggest accomplishment of 2022 was marrying the love of my life @evanrossell 
Something so easy felt like the biggest and hardest goal to reach for so many reasons but I’m glad as rushed and gunshot as it felt(planned in three months) ,that we stuck to our plan and got married this year. Looking forward to all our big plans and sharing the moment with extended friends and family in 2023 🏰🏆

One of the highlights of my year was being apart of @monsterenergy @javamonster as an artist for #artbasel as a #javamonsterpartner ;these film photos were shot at the end of our last night when we were closing down,it was packed the entire weekend and so much fun to give everyone a piece of @evanrossell and my art to each person at art Basel Miami who came to our booth. Also we got to see @coileray play privately for all the monster team. It was one of the best ways to end the year hands down #monster #monsterenergy #monsterenergygirls #monsterdrinkenergy #monsterenergype #javamonstercreator #javamonsterpartner
